Package: RGenEDA
Title: Genomic Exploratory Data Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Martinez", , "f007qps@dartmouth.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a unified and reproducible framework for performing genomic exploratory data analysis (EDA). Highly repetitive functions and analyses have been collated into an easy-to-use S4 object that produces quick results and customizable visualizations to assess variation in your data. See <https://github.com/mikemartinez99/RGenEDA>.
